T10TD4178E:34b-1: da sha ku sha l'a karma pa tha ni rde sha /
T10TD4178E:34b-3: mi dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam bstan pa /
T10TD4178E:34b-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T10TD4178E:34b-5: mi dge las kyi lam bcu ni //
T10TD4178E:34b-6: rang bzhin kha na tho bcas //
T10TD4178E:34b-7: bde ba don du gnyer ba yis //
T10TD4178E:34b-8: 'bad pa yis ni spang bar bya //
T10TD4178E:34b-9: bcu po de dag gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:34b-10: lus kyi dbye ba rnam gsum ste //
T10TD4178E:34b-11: ngag gi dbye ba rnam pa bzhi //
T10TD4178E:34b-12: yid kyi rab tu dbye ba gsum //
T10TD4178E:34b-13: mi dge bcu ru de dag 'dod //
T10TD4178E:34b-14: de rnams rab tu bshad par bya //
T10TD4178E:34b-15: de la re zhig lus kyis ni //
T10TD4178E:34b-16: srog gcod ma byin len log g-yem //
T10TD4178E:34b-17: ngag gi brdzun tshig phra ma dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-18: tshig rtsub dang ni 'khyal pa rnams //
T10TD4178E:34b-19: yid kyi log lta brnab sems gnod //
T10TD4178E:34b-20: de la srog gcod gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:34b-21: srog dang ldan par gyur pa la //
T10TD4178E:34b-22: srog dang ldan par 'du shes la //
T10TD4178E:34b-23: gnod sems nye bar gnas pa dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-24: rim pa bzhin du byas ldan dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-25: srog ni bcad par gyur pa st/ e / yan lag lnga po de dag dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-26: ldan ba srog gcod yin par bshad //
T10TD4178E:34b-27: ma byin len pa gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:34b-28: gzhan dag gi ni yin pa dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-29: gzhan gyis bdag gir byas pa dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-30: gzhan gyi yin par 'du shes dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-31: rku sems nye bar gnas pa dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-32: rim pa bzhin du byas ldan dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-33: gnas nas spags par gyur pa ste //
T10TD4178E:34b-34: yan lag drug po de dag dang //
T10TD4178E:34b-35: ldan pa ma byin len par bshad //
T10TD4178E:34b-36: de la log g-yem gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:34b-37: log par g-yem pa rnam bzhi ste //
T10TD4178E:35a-2: yan lag min dang bgrod min pa'o //
T10TD4178E:35a-3: de la'ang yul min bya ba ni //
T10TD4178E:35a-4: dam chos mchod rten sku gzugs dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-5: byang chub sems dpa'i bzhugs gnas stsogs //
T10TD4178E:35a-6: mkhan po dang ni slob dpon dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-7: pha ma drung na gnas ba ni //
T10TD4178E:35a-8: yul min de ru mi bya'o //
T10TD4178E:35a-9: de la dus min bya ba ni //
T10TD4178E:35a-10: zla mtshan 'dzag dang sbrum ma dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-11: bu chung dang bcas mi myos dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-12: sdug bsngal yid mi bde sogs dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-13: yan lag brgyad gnas dus min yin //
T10TD4178E:35a-14: yan lag min pa gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:35a-15: kha dang bshang lam byis pa dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-16: brlab bsdams lag pas bskyod pa yin //
T10TD4178E:35a-17: bgrod par bya min zhes bya ni //
T10TD4178E:35a-18: gzhan bzung chos kyi rgyal mtshan ldan //
T10TD4178E:35a-19: rigs kyis bsrungs dang rgyal mor gnas //
T10TD4178E:35a-20: gzhan gyis blangs dang smad 'tshong dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-21: nye du dag dang 'brel ba ni //
T10TD4178E:35a-22: de dag bgrod bya min pa yin //
T10TD4178E:35a-23: rnam pa de dag rnams la ni //
T10TD4178E:35a-24: rang gi chung ma bsten pa yang //
T10TD4178E:35a-26: brdzun du smra ba gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:35a-27: dngos po gnas par gyur pa dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-28: 'du shes gzhan du bsgyur ba dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-29: brdzun du smra bar gyur pa dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-30: rim pa bzhin du byas ldan dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-31: yan lag lnga po de dag dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-32: ldan pa brdzun du smra bar 'gyur //
T10TD4178E:35a-33: de la phra ma gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:35a-34: gzhan dag dbye phyir phra ma yin //
T10TD4178E:35a-35: de la tshig rtsub gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:35a-36: gzhan gyi gnad bsnun byed pa ni //
T10TD4178E:35a-37: yid du mi 'ong tshig smras yin //
T10TD4178E:35a-38: de la 'khyal ba gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:35a-39: 'dod pas nye bar blang ba dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-40: chags pa yid ni nyer bskyed nas //
T10TD4178E:35a-42: de la brnab sems gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:35a-43: gzhan gyi nor dang longs spyod la //
T10TD4178E:35a-44: mchog tu mngon bar chags pa yin //
T10TD4178E:35a-45: gnod sems zhes bya gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:35a-46: sems can rnams la sdang ba yis //
T10TD4178E:35a-47: rdeg dang 'ching dang gnod ba ste //
T10TD4178E:35a-48: de dag sems can la byed pa'o //
T10TD4178E:35a-49: log lta zhes bya gang zhe na //
T10TD4178E:35a-50: sbyin med mchod sbyin yod min dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-51: 'jig rten pha rol yod min dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-52: dge sbyong bram ze lha rnams med //
T10TD4178E:35a-53: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang dgra bcom dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-54: rang sangs rgyas dang legs spyod dang //
T10TD4178E:35a-55: nyes par spyod pa yod min zhes //
T10TD4178E:35a-56: bya ba log par lta ba yin //
T10TD4178E:35a-57: 'phags pa dran pa nyer gzhag dang//
T10TD4178E:35b-0: @35b thag ba chen po'i mdo rnams las //
T10TD4178E:35b-1: bcom ldan 'das kyis rgyas gsungs pa //
T10TD4178E:35b-2: 'di ni mdo ru bsdus pa yin //
T10TD4178E:35b-3: mi dge las kyi lam bcu ni //
T10TD4178E:35b-4: dmyal ba chen po'i rgyu ru bshad //
T10TD4178E:35b-5: dge bcu las kyi lam bsten pas //
T10TD4178E:35b-6: dmyal la sogs par ltung ma yin //
T10TD4178E:35b-7: sems can rnams la phan pa'i phyir //
T10TD4178E:35b-8: skye zhing skye ba rnams su ni //
T10TD4178E:35b-9: gang zhig skye ba las rgyal ba'i //
T10TD4178E:35b-10: byang chub rang bzhin des 'grub shog / mi dge bcu'i las kyi lam bstan pa zhes bya ba /
T10TD4178E:35b-11: slob dpon rta dbyangs kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T10TD4178E:35b-13: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po aa dzi ta shr'i bha dra dang /
T10TD4178E:35b-14: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba dge slong sh'akya 'od kyis bsgyur ba'o//
